# 🚀 UPIT – Visual Code Collaboration Platform

\

## 📌 Overview

UPIT is a full-stack web application that reimagines version control by replacing command-line workflows with an intuitive visual interface. It simplifies collaboration through drag-and-drop file management aSyeda Maria Fatimand flexible project modes.

## 🚀 Problem

Traditional version control systems like Git are powerful but complex for beginners, requiring command-line knowledge.

## 💡 Solution

UPIT provides a visual, user-friendly platform that allows developers to manage code and collaborate without using commands.

## 🎯 Impact

* Simplifies collaboration for beginners
* Reduces learning curve of version control
* Enables faster project management

---

## ✨ Features

* Drag-and-drop file upload & management
* Solo / Group mode switching
* Public / Private project visibility
* Clean and responsive UI

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

* **Frontend:** React.js, Bootstrap
* **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
* **Database:** MongoDB
* **Auth:** Passport.js
* **Tools:** Axios, UUID

---

## ⚙️ Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/SamiAbdulWajid/Sami-s-UPIT.git
cd Sami-s-UPIT
npm install
npm start
```

---

## 📌 Future Improvements

* Version history tracking
